This projeect is garbaje and should not be used as material for learing OpenGL.
However, if someone is capable of using and understanding anything then go for it.

To Build the project:
  * make an empty project in visual studio
  * drop all files and folders inside.
  * Change the additional include directories of the project to include the GLFW and Glew folders(properties -> C/C++ -> General ->Additional Include Directories)
  * Change the linker to include glew32s.lib, glfw3.lib, & opengl32.lib
